# 通过指定的路径、文件名和架构名自动探测是否存在架构相关的文件，如果有则返回架构相关的文件内容，如果没有则返回指定路径和文件名的文件内容。
# 参数1: 指定的路径名
# 参数2: 指定的文件名
# 参数3: 指定的架构名
# 返回: 文件的内容
# 说明: 在查找指定架构相关文件时的搜索方式：${1}/arch/${3}/${2}对应的文件。

function cat_arch_file
{
	declare CAT_PATH="${1}"
	declare CAT_FILE="${2}"
	declare CAT_ARCH="${3}"
#	echo "${1}/arch/${CAT_ARCH}/${2}" >> /tmp/a.log
	if [ -f ${1}/arch/${CAT_ARCH}/${2} ]; then
		if [ "x${PACKAGE_VERSION}" == "x" ]; then
			echo "$(cat ${1}/arch/${CAT_ARCH}/${2} | grep -v "^#[[:blank:]]")"
		else
			get_body_with_version ${1}/arch/${CAT_ARCH}/${2} "${PACKAGE_VERSION}"
		fi
	else
		if [ -f ${1}/Settings/${2} ]; then
			if [ "x${PACKAGE_VERSION}" == "x" ]; then
				echo "$(cat ${1}/Settings/${2} | grep -v "^#[[:blank:]]")"
			else
				get_body_with_version ${1}/Settings/${2} "${PACKAGE_VERSION}"
			fi
		else
			if [ -f ${1}/${2} ]; then
	                        if [ "x${PACKAGE_VERSION}" == "x" ]; then
        	                        echo "$(cat ${1}/${2} | grep -v "^#[[:blank:]]")"
	                        else
        		                get_body_with_version ${1}/${2} "${PACKAGE_VERSION}"
                        	fi
			else
				echo ""
			fi
		fi
	fi
}


#格式化组设置字符串
function format_one_opt_str
{
	declare STEP_OPT="${1}"
	declare OPT_FLAG="${2}"
	declare OPT_STEP_NAME="${3}"
	declare -a RET_OPT
	declare RET_OPT_COUNT=0
	declare APPEND_OPT=""
	for opt in $(echo ${STEP_OPT} | tr "+" "\\n")
	do
		case "${opt}" in
		opt)
			RET_OPT[${RET_OPT_COUNT}]="${OPT_FLAG}_${opt}"
			;;
		bad)
			RET_OPT[${RET_OPT_COUNT}]="${OPT_FLAG}_${OPT_STEP_NAME}_${opt}"
			;;
		\&*)
			RET_OPT[${RET_OPT_COUNT}]="${OPT_FLAG}_${opt:1}"
			;;
		\**)
			RET_OPT[${RET_OPT_COUNT}]="${OPT_FLAG}_${OPT_STEP_NAME}_${opt:1}"
			;;
		*)
			if [ "x${opt}" != "x" ]; then
				RET_OPT[${RET_OPT_COUNT}]="${opt}"
			else
				continue
			fi
			;;
		esac
		((RET_OPT_COUNT++))
	done
	APPEND_OPT="$(IFS='+'; echo "${RET_OPT[*]}")"
	echo "${APPEND_OPT}"

}

#格式化组设置字符串
function format_group_opt_str
{
	declare STEP_OPT="${1}"
	declare OPT_FLAG="${2}"
	declare OPT_STEP_NAME="${3}"
	declare -a RET_OPT
	declare RET_OPT_COUNT=0
	declare APPEND_OPT=""
	for opt in $(echo ${STEP_OPT} | tr "," "\\n")
	do
		if [ "x${opt}" != "x" ]; then
			RET_OPT[${RET_OPT_COUNT}]=$(format_one_opt_str "${opt}" "${OPT_FLAG}" "${OPT_STEP_NAME}")
		else
			continue
		fi
		((RET_OPT_COUNT++))
	done

	APPEND_OPT="$(IFS=','; echo "${RET_OPT[*]}")"
	echo "${APPEND_OPT}"
}

